Base.Explanation: List the documents in the specified printer queue.

ArrayElement.Name: Printer
ArrayElement.Description: The name of printer or print server queue. Syntax: \\ComputerName\PrinterName. Example: \\SERVER_A\LaserPrinter439

ArrayElement.Name: Documents table
ArrayElement.Description: Specify the name of the output variable (default: %DocumentsTable%) that will hold a table with the information of the documents when the action is executed.
